        public AlertInfo(String id,
                 long limit,
                 String sql,
                 boolean enabled,
                 @Nullable
                 String notificationSubject,
                 @Nullable
                 String notificationBody)
        Creates new alert.
        Parameters:
        id - the alert unique identification
        limit - limit that must be exceeded to activate alert
        sql - SQL query that returns count of items for comparison with limit value
        enabled - if specified alert is enabled or disabled
        notificationSubject - the (mail, sms) subject
        notificationBody - the (mail, sms) body
